# Wokki backend

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md), [docs/README.md](../../docs/README.md), [docs/brd.md](../../docs/brd.md), [docs/business-rules.md](../../docs/business-rules.md), [docs/architecture.md](../../docs/architecture.md), [docs/minimal-api.md](../../docs/minimal-api.md). BRD tiếng Việt: [docs/vi/README.md](../../docs/vi/README.md). Enforce locked rules (`BR-xxx`); do not contradict [docs/process-flows.md](../../docs/process-flows.md) (or [docs/vi/process-flows.md](../../docs/vi/process-flows.md)).

## API modules

- One file: `src/Wokki.Api/Apis/{Feature}/{Feature}Endpoints.cs`
- `MapXxxApi()` + `MapXxxRoutes()` + private static handlers
- Register in `Bootstrapping/PipelineExtensions.MapEndpoints()`
- Base path: `/api/v1/{resource}` (except `/health`)
- `.AllowAnonymous()` or `.RequireAuthorization()` / `.RequireRole(RoleConstants.Admin)`
- `.Produces<ApiResponse<T>>(...)` and `.Produces<ApiResponse<object>>(400/401/403/...)`
- Validate: `request.ValidateRequest(validator, out var validationResult)` then `return validationResult!`
- Response: `return (await service.Method(...)).ToHttpResult();`
- Every route must include: `.WithName(...)`, `.WithDescription(...)`, `.Produces(...)`
- Apply rate limit at group level: `.RequireRateLimiting("Fixed")`
- Register every new module in `PipelineExtensions.MapEndpoints()` in the same change

## Layers

Domain (entities, repos, `RoleConstants`) → Application (services, DTOs, validators) → Infrastructure (EF, JWT) → Api (HTTP only).

## Application structure (mandatory)

- `src/Wokki.Application/Dtos/{Auth|User|...}`
- `src/Wokki.Application/Services/{Feature}/Interfaces`
- `src/Wokki.Application/Services/{Feature}/Implementations`
- `src/Wokki.Application/Validators/{Feature}`
- `src/Wokki.Application/Mappings/{Feature}`
- Do not create or reintroduce `src/Wokki.Application/Features/*`
- Namespace must follow folder path (`Wokki.Application.Dtos.Auth`, `Wokki.Application.Services.User.Interfaces`, etc.)

## Commands (Taskfile)

Agents **must** use `task` from repo root (`Taskfile.yml`): `task build`, `task docker:build`, `task migration:update`, etc. See [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md). Do not substitute raw `docker compose` / `dotnet ef` when a task exists.

## Guardrails

- Never add business logic, EF queries, or token generation inside `Wokki.Api`
- Never inject `DbContext` into `Wokki.Application`
- Never return raw entities from API; always map DTOs and `ApiResponse<T>`
- Before finishing any task: `task build` (build gate) and ensure no namespace drift from the structure above
